      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to put my pride and joy up for sale. This car is in truly incredible, like-new condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, it's always been garaged, and the interior is still spotless. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to enjoy it. You really won't find another one this clean! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come see it or have any questions. Can't wait to hear from you!",
