    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, optimized by a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The drivetrain features the coveted Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable Lock differential. This chassis is structurally pristine, with a verified subframe and all mechanical tolerances meeting original factory specifications. Every bushing, seal, and gasket remains in peak operational condition. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original luster with zero oxidation. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
