    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition, appearing as though it has been frozen in time. The exterior boasts a flawless, deep-gloss finish with a professional ceramic coating that provides a mirror-like reflection; there are no stone chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks in the paint. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of 'like-new' luxury. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every surface, from the genuine wood inlays to the brushed aluminum accents, is free of scratches or oils. All technological features, including the panoramic infotainment display and the premium surround-sound system, operate with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a documented history of preventative care. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
